721400f.title: Manhattan: Madison Avenue - 57th Street
721400f.text:
A general view north on Madison Ave. from East 57th Street. Note Central Park on the left with Central Park West dimly observable with the twin towers of the San Remo (Apartment House) thereon. Silhouetted against the Park (left foreground) is the sloped roof of the Savoy-Plasa IIotel. On the right appears the chimney of the electric generating plant of the Consolidated Gas Company (East 92nd Street at the East River).
About 1930.
International News Photos.
